{"tid":667222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普twitter發文 要求中國作更多讓步","createTime":"2018-05-16T14:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T17:58:10.000Z","uid":83582,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a424d309c22b59a4b5e43943c31b93dbbde96c36","tid":667222,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"2018年05月16日<br />\n<br />\n特朗普於twitter發文，指中興通訊(763)涉及較大的貿易協議，中美貿易已令美國每年損失數千億美元。<br />\n<br />\n他指以往美國政府在談判中表現欠佳。而中國已經看到美國的要求。他重申談判還未開始，直指美國可以讓步的已經不多，因為多年來已經給予太多，中國需要更多貢獻(because it has given so much over the years. China has much to give!)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58201435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58201435&d=UqDTeOLwe1JSaJPeU29b74zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6496a376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58201435&h=75bbdb6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58201435</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter原文:<br />\n <br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n1 hour ago<br />\n<br />\n...haven&rsquo;t even started yet! The U.S. has very little to give, because it has given so much over the years. China has much to give!"},{"pid":"23346257b4894240ae4aa13f6061b70fa0858c1f","tid":667222,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解冇人睇呢個post架 五毛呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113bf66ea68622a69094ff3c361e8bd029bfa914","tid":667222,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"其實佢依個post似為咗攻擊民主黨多啲，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a074d314b9b365fadb8d73a0f2592c7b56c8d18f","tid":667222,"uid":48083,"like":2,